{"tid":1821012,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【武漢爆疫症】直擊廣州野味店蛇鼠孔雀照賣 雞犬同困無懼交叉感染","createTime":"2020-01-12T02:45:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-12T09:09:36.000Z","uid":130626,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"a0028a8527029e19e65dddbee577fca7856d1549","tid":1821012,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T02:45:31.000Z","msg":"2003年非典型肺炎一疫後，廣東嚴打野味交易，惟一直掃之不盡。在「地頭蛇」引路下，《蘋果》在廣州市區尋獲一家野味飯店，供客享用田鼠、竹鼠、眼鏡蛇，甚至樹熊。另在一個大型乾濕貨市場，也有野雞、野鴨等較為尋常的野味出售，武漢不明肺炎，似乎無礙食野味的興致。<br />\n<br />\n記者當日佯稱幫老闆探路找野味，獲的士司機帶到天河區的野味飯店。該飯店無明顯招牌，隱身於一條丘徑的末端，相當隱蔽，從廣州南站出發，車程近一小時。司機笑指：「如果冇熟人帶路，我都唔知你點搵」。<br />\n<br />\n飯店頗為殘破，廚房骯髒不堪，有老鼠「搵食」。飯店當時正值下午落場，只有一名廚房阿姐在客廳玩手機。記者上前探問：「我替老闆找野味，聽說這裏有。」阿姐明白記者來意後稱：「有竹鼠、田鼠、樹熊、孔雀等等，孔雀可以炆也可以打火鍋，大概1,000元人民幣（約1,120港元）一隻」。<br />\n<br />\n在記者要求看一看野味「合不合老闆口味」，另一名職員打開儲物倉，倉內十餘個小鐵籠分別困住田鼠、竹鼠合共三、四隻、十多條眼鏡蛇、水魚、鱷龜。眼鏡蛇為158元人民幣一斤（約180港元）。男子向記者稱「野的」，隨後便匆匆關閘，記者也隨即乘的士離開。<br />\n<br />\n回程時，司機稱以前野味主要在江南的市場銷售，經整頓後已大減，「要去到從化，50、60公里外先搵到&hellip;&hellip;你食多幾次，同佢熟絡之後，佢有野味賣就會打畀你。」<br />\n<br />\n記者同日到頗具規模的東圃農貿市場視察，衞生環境比較差，地下水迹、污迹較多。市場數家活禽檔口都有野雞、野鴨、野鴿、田鼠等野味出售。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G0K7VC3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG0K7VC3.jpg&h=6e44d4f4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ObLV4wq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FObLV4wq.jpg&h=1c7e688c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20200112/60473904\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20200112%2F60473904&d=uClJ75VMDgyJ2T8QnpTVXQg0DHywPMniAnH04N%2BeXdM%3D&h=af3547c2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20200112%2F60473904&h=45a6e163\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20200112/60473904</a>"},{"pid":"33b887a792f615de7b1b934f65a65e069c268ec1","tid":1821012,"uid":131522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T02:57:49.000Z","msg":"孔雀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07f043d0c6901390a103f7e65dcd8bbb31542ce9","tid":1821012,"uid":177089,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T03:21:20.000Z","msg":"老老實實 澳洲咁撚多野生怪物 如果俾支那人全部轉移過去實食到成個島無咗"},{"pid":"e7d0d0d499713cfdfcaa172e853b90d633b91d97","tid":1821012,"uid":328506,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T03:26:40.000Z","msg":"樹熊都有？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點食得落口呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb0070475bc513d559d91032151d510d63f18fb5","tid":1821012,"uid":249160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T03:36:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c233253fee1235eaf17f5de2dd1d1fa43ebe7db","tid":1821012,"uid":27946,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T03:39:20.000Z","msg":"咁撚多野食點解一定要吃呢d<br />\n痴撚線國家"},{"pid":"c7732da440ce70f1d8a9ea194ae25e7748a63239","tid":1821012,"uid":54264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T03:39:56.000Z","msg":"孔雀可以炆也可以打火鍋，大概1,000元人民幣（約1,120港元）一隻<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be6168fa11ad08effc89690da47d59ed7764964e","tid":1821012,"uid":6192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T03:42:06.000Z","msg":"屌d生蕃乜撚都放入口<br />\n自己死就好喇 <br />\n唔好撚累人喇"},{"pid":"b153ce65f4d3c514f61ebfa30e8191dc7da42acd","tid":1821012,"uid":268519,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T03:42:15.000Z","msg":"孔雀樹熊都放入口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/91isVW2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail